{"id":212030,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/02/归真堂开通微博账号-网友抗议齐呼滚/","date":"2012-02-24T10:45:03Z","modified":"2012-07-30T18:36:13Z","title":"归真堂开通微博账号 网友抗议齐呼“滚”","content":"<p>归真堂今日在新浪微博开通了认证账号后遭网友围观，众多用户在其微博下排队齐呼&ldquo;滚&rdquo;。</p>\n<p>以下截图来自新浪微博用户@作业本：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@作业本：兲朝著名企业：@归真堂 ，微博开通一小时后&hellip;&hellip;这是继红十字会开通微博以来，微博史上极为罕见的又一次站队&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/48bc2ad4jw1dqco76qvwmj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"2840\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/48bc2ad4jw1dqco76qvwmj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"2840\" /></p>\n<p>名为&ldquo;<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/1987987811\">大尸凶</a>&rdquo;的网友就该事件迅速创作了一幅漫画：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/02/guizhentang.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"579\" height=\"690\" /></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[17016,9203,20534],"tags":[13853,15465,9991,19215]}